table.name: mts_basket_flow_info
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_basket_flow_info', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(flow_time) ORDER BY (flow_time, flow_equipment_code, track_in) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_basket_read_detail
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_basket_read_detail', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(read_time) ORDER BY (uid, rfid, eq_code, read_time, basket_on_site, rfid_read, uid_read) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192 COMMENT '花篮读取详情'

table.name: mts_boat_flow_info
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_boat_flow_info', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(flow_time) ORDER BY (flow_time, boat_code, process_unit_code) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_equipment_running
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_equipment_running', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(report_time) ORDER BY (process_code, unit_code, plc_code, eq_code, point_code, report_time) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192 COMMENT 'DWS层设备运行参数'

table.name: mts_flow_log
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_flow_log', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(process_time) ORDER BY (process_time, model_type, collect_time, equipment_code) TTL toDateTime(process_time) + toIntervalDay(3) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_issue_log
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_issue_log', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(process_time) ORDER BY (process_time, model_type, collect_time, equipment_code) TTL toDateTime(process_time) + toIntervalDay(7) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_middle_points_local
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_middle_points_local', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(collect_time) ORDER BY (collect_time, equip_code, plc_code) TTL toDateTime(collect_time) + toIntervalDay(3) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_middle_pre_local
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_middle_pre_local', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMM(collect_time) ORDER BY (collect_time, equip_code, process_code) TTL toDateTime(collect_time) + toIntervalDay(3) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_process_info
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_process_info', '{replica}') ORDER BY (code, sort_number) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192 COMMENT '工序信息'

table.name: mts_wafer_flow_bind
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_wafer_flow_bind_new', '{replica}') PARTITION BY (toYYYYMMDD(flow_up_time), flow_process_code) ORDER BY (wafer_id, flow_up_time, batch_code, batch_order_no) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_wafer_flow_info
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_wafer_flow_info_new', '{replica}') PARTITION BY (toYYYYMMDD(flow_up_time), flow_process_code) ORDER BY (wafer_id, flow_up_time, batch_code, batch_order_no) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192

table.name: mts_wafer_iv_check
table.EngineParams: ('/clickhouse/tables/{shard}/mts/mts_wafer_iv_check-2', '{replica}') PARTITION BY toYYYYMMDD(test_date) ORDER BY (wafer_id, batch_order_no, batch_code) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192
